      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably preserved vehicle, a specimen that represents the zenith of its production year. This automobile has been maintained to a standard that transcends the typical pre-owned market, appearing in showroom condition both aesthetically and mechanically. The exterior finish remains deep and lustrous, while the interior retains its original factory integrity, free of any discernible wear. This is an exemplary opportunity for the discerning collector or professional to acquire a vehicle of uncompromising quality and fastidious provenance.",
